{"tid":901452,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個先係真正既日出之國?","createTime":"2018-11-14T04:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T04:36:33.000Z","uid":205143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df5684788f95b43fd08662e3d4f150d9c15c8ed9","tid":901452,"uid":205143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T04:32:52.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，太陽由東邊升起，故此日本作為過去所知最東邊既國家，亦被稱為日出之國。但地球係圓既，日本東方仲有美國，美國東方則係歐洲，咁到底邊個先真正稱得上係日出之國?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acef10878ab67b12ab6e16989d5a87b517c7010","tid":901452,"uid":200781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紅太陽之國"}]}